These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, old-henry, vegafina
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, spy, drama
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, zinnia, iris
3 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, poker
City: hannover, marseilles, london
 1. the person traveling to hannover is the person playing scrabble##1
 2. the person traveling to london is the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person playing poker and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is the vegafina-smoker##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person playing bridge##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 9. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Cigar          | old-henry       | vegafina    | bongani         |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking        |
| Movie-Genre           | romance | spy   | drama      |
| Flower   | zinnia        | iris    | sunflower       |
| Game   | scrabble     | bridge  | poker       |
| City         | hannover     | marseilles | london |

