House: palace, cottage, cape-cod
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, disaster
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, may, july
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, architect, videographer
3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, pony
3 different games are played: snooker, monopoly, whist
 1. the owner of the pony is the architect##1
 2. the owner of the pony is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the person playing snooker is between the person driving the bus and the person driving the train##2
 5. the videographer is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the bus is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 8. the palace house is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Transport      | train   | tram    | bus         |
| House          | palace    | cottage | cape-cod          |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | disaster  | animation     |
| Birthday   | july       | may      | october         |
| Job   | videographer      | architect   | designer    |
| Pet           | dog        | pony      | horse         |
| Game         | monopoly | snooker  | whist |

