 1. the person who likes pink is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of techno is in the middle##1
 3. the victorian house is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 4. the person eating carrot is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the victorian house##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person who growszinnia is between the fan of rock and the futuristic house##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person who growsdahlia##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the person who growsdahlia is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre      | rock | techno      | hip-hop      |
| Food         | asparagus     | strawberry     | carrot  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| House   | wooden  | victorian     | futuristic |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Color         | lavender    | pink | orange   |
| Flower     | tulip        | zinnia        | dahlia   |

