.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different games are played: poker, chess, monopoly
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, february, january
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, british, japanese
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, manager, musician
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, pokersy, iris
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, gospel, dubstep
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, skateboard
1. the person playing chess is on the left of the musician##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the dressmaker##1
4. the fan of jazz is between the person who growsbellflower and the manager##2
5. the person who's birthday is in january is between the musician and the japanese##2
6. the british is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person playing chess##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
9. the person who growspokersy is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Game      | poker      | chess      | monopoly       |
| Birthday          | february      | january    | july   |
| Nationality         | japanese    | egyptian     | british     |
| Job           | manager    | dressmaker | musician   |
| Flower   | pokersy    | iris    | bellflower       |
| Music-Genre         | dubstep | jazz      | gospel    |
| Transport     | ship       | helicopter | skateboard |

