.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, fisherman, coach
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, peach, zucchini
There are 3 different nationalities: german, malaysian, australian
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, bellflower, azalea
House: cottage, victorian, wooden
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, fonseca, old-henry
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is the malaysian##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
5. the person eating peach is between the coach and the german##2
6. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the wooden house##1
7. the writer is on the right of the victorian house##1
8. the person driving the motorbike is the person who growsazalea##1
9. the german is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Job      | coach       | writer     | fisherman         |
| Food          | lettuce     | peach      | zucchini     |
| Nationality         | malaysian | australian    | german      |
| Flower   | rose   | bellflower | azalea    |
| House   | victorian        | wooden     | cottage   |
| Cigar         | oliveros     | fonseca | old-henry |
| Transport     | scooter     | ship       | motorbike    |

