.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
House: cottage, wooden, tower
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, punk, funk
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, fisherman, nurse
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, french, italian
City: hannover, rome, paris
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, grey, emerald
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, horror, scientific
1. the cottage house is the fan of funk##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is the person who likes apricot##1
3. the dressmaker is between the tower house and the person traveling to paris##2
4. the canadian is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the fisherman is the fan of r&b##1
8. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
9. the french is between the fan of r&b and the person watching animation movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| House      | wooden    | cottage       | tower      |
| Music-Genre          | r&b   | funk   | punk  |
| Job           | fisherman  | dressmaker | nurse    |
| Nationality   | canadian   | french     | italian  |
| City           | paris     | hannover        | rome |
| Color         | grey | apricot   | emerald  |
| Movie-Genre     | horror    | scientific     | animation      |

 